OL,3,CProposed school closure put on hold
OL,4,Cfollowing council consultation
OL,6,FA Council's proposal to close schools
OL,7,Fon North Tyneside has been put on hold.
OL,9,FThis comes after discussions on the
OL,10,Fproposals to merge four other schools
OL,11,Fare however set to enter the next
OL,12,Fstage.
OL,14,FNorth Tyneside Council announced this
OL,15,Fafternoon (26 November) the results of
OL,16,Fits six-week consultation, in one of
OL,17,Fthe biggest proposed overhauls to
OL,18,Flocal education in decades.
