OL,3,CProposed school closure put on hold
OL,4,Cfollowing council consultation
OL,6,FIt confirmed the proposed closure of
OL,7,FMonkseaton Middle School and a merger
OL,8,Fof Appletree Gardens First School and
OL,9,FLangley First School would be paused
OL,10,Fto explore alternative options put
OL,11,Fforward by the consultation.
OL,13,FHowever, controversial plans to merge
OL,14,Fother schools are set to move forward.
