OL,3,CProposed school closure put on hold
OL,4,Cfollowing council consultation
OL,6,FThe mergers of Hazlewood with
OL,7,FGreenfields Primary School and Ivy
OL,8,FRoad with Forest Hall Primary will now
OL,9,Fbe subject to a new statutory
OL,10,Fconsultation, which is the next stage
OL,11,Fof the formal process required for the
OL,12,Freorganisation.
OL,14,FLocal officials have argued that a
OL,15,Fdeclining birth rate, equating to 300
OL,16,Ffewer births year on year since 2018/
OL,17,F2019, and the knock-on impacts for
OL,18,Fschool budgets and vacant places mean
OL,19,Fthat changes are needed.
