OL,3,CProposed school closure put on hold
OL,4,Cfollowing council consultation
OL,6,FThe original proposals resulted in an
OL,7,Foutcry among parents, sparking
OL,8,Fpetitions and the raising of funds for
OL,9,Fpotential legal challenges.
OL,11,FDirector of children's services at
OL,12,FNorth Tyneside Council Julie Firth
OL,13,Fsaid: "We have seen an incredible
OL,14,Flevel of passion and commitment from
OL,15,Fthese communities, and I want to thank
OL,16,Feveryone who has taken the time to
OL,17,Fshare their views and explore
OL,18,Falternatives.
