OL,3,CProposed school closure put on hold
OL,4,Cfollowing council consultation
OL,6,F"We are encouraged that through this
OL,7,Fengagement, potential viable options
OL,8,Fhave emerged for Monkseaton Middle
OL,9,FSchool and Langley First School. To
OL,10,Fensure these options are fully
OL,11,Fexplored, we have paused the proposals
OL,12,Ffor these schools.
OL,14,F"For the proposed mergers of Hazlewood
OL,15,FPrimary and Greenfields Primary, and
OL,16,FIvy Road Primary and Forest Hall
OL,17,FPrimary, no viable alternative options
OL,18,Fwere identified.
