OL,6,F"The decision therefore has been taken
OL,7,Fto move to statutory consultation and
OL,8,Fis now subject to a five-day call-in
OL,9,Fperiod.
OL,11,F"It is planned for the statutory
OL,12,Fconsultation to begin on Thursday 4
OL,13,FDecember and it will run for four
OL,14,Fweeks."
